Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.28,0:00:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur10}Do you know...\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}知道么…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}that the only dog ever struck by lightning was right here, in Egypt?\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}史上唯一一只被闪电击中的狗就在埃及？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}I wish I'd met you before we were dead.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}真希望我能在死之前遇见你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}You know, technically...\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}从理论上讲…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}we could cross off two items:\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}我们一次实现了两项愿望{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}"See the pyramids"...\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}看看金字塔{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}and "witness something majestic."\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}以及"亲眼目睹神迹"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}This is about as majestic as it gets.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}眼前的奇观已经近乎神迹了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}Wait till you see my mountain.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}等你看到我的神山再说吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}Oh, yeah.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}哦 是啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}Your mountain.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}你的神山{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}Still, this ain't half bad.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}这个已经非常不错了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}You know, the ancient Egyptians had a beautiful belief about death.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}知道么 古埃及人对死亡有种美好的信念{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}When their souls got to the entrance to heaven, the gods asked them two questions.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}当他们的灵魂到了天堂门口, 他们的神们会问他们两个问题{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}Their answers determined whether they were admitted or not.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}天堂的门是否开放 取决于问题的答案{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}Okay, I'll bite.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}好吧 我来试试{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}What were they?\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}是什么问题？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}Have you found joy in your life?\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}在你的生命中 是否有过快乐？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}Answer the question.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}回答我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.90,0:01:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}- Me? - Yeah, you. - Answer the question, "Have I found joy in my life?" - Yes.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}- 我么？- 是的 就是你。 - 问题是"我的生命中有没有快乐？" - 没错{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}Yes.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}Has your life brought joy to others?\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}那你这一生有没有给别人带去快乐？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}Ah, this type of question, I...\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}呃 这样的问题 我…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}I don't know, uh...\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}我不知道…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}I don't think about how other people gauge, uh...\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}不知别人心里是怎么想的 所以…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}Ask them.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}问他们去吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}I'm asking you.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}我问的是你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}Fine.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}好罢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur9}Fine.\N{\fs24\3c&HE080E0&}好罢{\r}
